LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:流动方程：Euler：非守恒型：一维"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

）比守恒型（式 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:流动方程：Euler：守恒型：三维"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 或式 
